Package com.flipkart.business

Interface ProfessorInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
ProfessorOperations
public interface ProfessorInterface
Interface representing the operations available to a Professor. Provides methods to view courses, students, and to grade students.

  • Method Details

    • viewCourses

      void viewCourses(int professorId)
      Retrieves and displays the list of courses available to the professor.
      Parameters:
      professorId - The ID of the professor requesting to view courses. This method should display all courses assigned to or available for the professor.

    • viewStudents

      void viewStudents(int professorId)
      Retrieves and displays the list of students associated with the professor.
      Parameters:
      professorId - The ID of the professor requesting to view students. This method should display all students taught by or related to the professor.

    • gradeStudent

      void gradeStudent(int professorId, int studentId, int courseId)
      Assigns a grade to a student for a specific course.
      Parameters:
      professorId - The ID of the professor assigning the grade.
      studentId - The ID of the student who is receiving the grade.
      courseId - The ID of the course for which the grade is being assigned. This method should update the student's grade for the specified course.
